channel.title: Run server Port already in use?
channel.description:
I have been trying to figure this problem out for about 1-2 weeks, and nobody seems to understand what i mean when i say, ' when i run my server it says server already in use' and all people say is check too see if you have it running already, which i dont.
So what i am asking is for someone to get on my computer from teamviewer, i mean idk what happend. at first my cmd froze but then i re-installed a newer version of mysql, and now the cmd doesnt freeze, now the port is in use all the time,no matter if i change the port to 5555. or even if i restart my computer, so someone PLEASE just let me know if you wanna help over teamviewer (someone experienced) , and i'd be glad to PMyou the teamviewer details. thank's!
